{"tid":1736841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！有冇人知呢幾架旅遊巴去左邊間警署","createTime":"2019-11-18T20:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T22:01:24.000Z","uid":339530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25d489ff51e9583467a69823b006034ebde85f7f","tid":1736841,"uid":339530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:52:38.000Z","msg":"//2:12 於 #油麻地 港鐵A1出口外，防暴拘捕約六至七十名黑衣示威者。現場所見，防暴先把已拘捕的示威者以索帶扣緊雙手，再押至分色帶劃分的區域內，與醫護人員及市民分隔。期間，警方不斷以強光照射被補者樣貌。其後，警方以三部旅遊巴將所有扣捕者送走，而運送的旅遊巴車牌為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">UT2736、RM819及AM8818</span></span>。<br />\n-<br />\n記者： SF Yeung@STP<br />\n發聲社新聞 STP MEDIA<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stpmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpmedia&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c936f4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stpmedia</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/singthepress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fsingthepress&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=b08c5c8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/singthepress</a>"},{"pid":"548bd49e2bc85978b28a49c513a9dcbdc54657f5","tid":1736841,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T21:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45f0b69cbbd093019b89ec8912b03f48f9cac07d","tid":1736841,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T21:23:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae2299634a3cf53c0c7d2d76e6bdcecdf7c300f7","tid":1736841,"uid":339530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T21:47:26.000Z","msg":"求下大家幫手<br />\n我朋友俾人拉左"},{"pid":"2be980c4950d2dcd2cbdef1b18e6c95543e9787f","tid":1736841,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T21:56:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.m